divs: Sighting Details This is not the first sighting. We have seen itoff and on for the past two months approximately. It is mid evening and themoon is bright and the sky is clear. The object is in the same place...high inthe eastern sky. This is an island in the ocean so it may be over water. Withour binoculars we can see definitely the green and then red flickering. Theobject is stationary but thered and green lights and in a sequence of some sort.THe red light is much brighter than the green.
Summary: Flashing red and green star like entity
